          "reviewBody": "We went 19Aug 2023 for bank exam.\nRoad under construction in front of school it's good aproach from Periferal express way and pataudi road cuts each other.0be careful on roads due to huge vehical on the road there may be ware houses adani etc.\nThere is adjoining Petrol pump to the school",
