            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "One can reach here for competitive exams by:-\nFirst, take metro to M.G Road, from there take auto/bus to reach gurgaon bus stand  and from there 3 options are available.\n1. Take bus from either bus stand or Mahavir chowk/ Gaushala ground bus stand going to pataudi, get down at jhankar high school (they will charge around 20rs.)\n2. Take shared auto to hayatpur/wazirpur chowk and then take another auto to jhankar high school.\n3. Take direct auto to jhankar high school.\n\nLocker facilities- either deposit outside for 20rs Or place inside the school in the rack (at your own risk)\n\nFor washrooms/ toilets, one can use nearby petrol pump washrooms as no facility provided outside the school.",
